# Plan Tái Cấu Trúc Quản Lý UI

## Persistence Model

| Manager | Type | Lý do |
|---------|------|-------|
| [GameManager](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/GameManager.cs#6-37) | **Persistence** | Game state, player data xuyên scene |
| `AudioManager` | **Persistence** | Nhạc chơi liên tục |
| `CoinManager` | **Persistence** ⚠️ cần fix | Coin persist giữa Home ↔ Dungeon |
| [UIManager](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/UIManager.cs#7-194) | **Singleton** (scene-bound) | Mỗi scene có UI riêng, destroy khi chuyển scene |
| [MenuManager](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/MenuManager.cs#7-263) | **Singleton** (scene-bound) | Chỉ dùng ở HomeScene |
| [UISystem](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/UISystem.cs#9-69) | MonoBehaviour (scene-bound) | Audio panel UI, mỗi scene instance riêng |

> [!NOTE]
> `CoinManager` hiện là [Singleton](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/Singleton.cs#3-12) → bị destroy khi chuyển scene. Cần chuyển sang [Persistence](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/Singleton.cs#13-21).

