## Phase 1: Loại bỏ Duplicate Event Subscriptions

#### [MODIFY] [UIManager.cs](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/UIManager.cs)

Xóa 4 direct subscriptions trong `OnEnable/OnDisable`, chỉ giữ UIEvents:

```diff
 private void OnEnable()
 {
-    LevelManager.OnRoomCompleted += RoomCompleted;
-    LevelManager.OnPlayerInRoomBoss += ShowHealthUIBoss;
-    PlayerWeapon.OnShowUIWeaponEvent += ShowUIWeapon;
-    PlayerVitality.OnPlayerDeathEvent += ShowGameOverPanel;
     UIEvents.OnPlayerStatsChanged += OnPlayerStatsChanged;
     // ... giữ nguyên UIEvents subscriptions
 }
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Verify rằng [LevelManager](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/LevelManager.cs#8-379), `PlayerWeapon`, `PlayerVitality` đã fire UIEvents tương ứng. Nếu chưa → thêm `UIEvents.OnXxx?.Invoke()`.

