## Phase 2: Tách Trách Nhiệm

#### [NEW] [SceneNavigator.cs](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/SceneNavigator.cs)

Tách scene navigation ra khỏi [UISystem](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/UISystem.cs#9-69):

```csharp
public class SceneNavigator : MonoBehaviour
{
    public void StartGame()
    {
        if (Time.timeScale == 0) return;
        SceneManager.LoadScene("HomeScene");
    }
    public void ReturnToStart()
    {
        GameManager.Instance.playerPrefab = null;
        SceneManager.LoadScene("StartScene");
    }
    public void QuitGame() => Application.Quit();
}
```

#### [MODIFY] [UISystem.cs](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/UISystem.cs)

Xóa [StartGame()](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/UISystem.cs#58-64), [ReturnHomeScene()](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/UISystem.cs#52-57), [QuitGame()](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/UISystem.cs#64-68) → đã chuyển sang `SceneNavigator`. Chỉ giữ audio logic.

#### [MODIFY] [MenuManager.cs](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/MenuManager.cs)

- Xóa [ShowUIWeapon()](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/MenuManager.cs#95-103) + fields (`weaponPanel`, `weaponImage`, `energyConsumptionText`)
- Xóa [Update()](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Player/PlayerController.cs#45-61) polling coin
- Xóa `PlayerWeapon.OnShowUIWeaponEvent += ShowUIWeapon` trong [EnableMovement()](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/MenuManager.cs#74-94)
- Subscribe `UIEvents.OnCoinChanged` để update coin text event-driven

