## Phase 3: Thống nhất UIEvents Bus

#### [MODIFY] [CoinManager.cs](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/CoinManager.cs)

- Chuyển từ [Singleton](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/Singleton.cs#3-12) → [Persistence](file:///d:/GameTopDown/GameTopDown/Assets/Scripts/Manager/Singleton.cs#13-21) (persist data giữa scenes)
- Fire `UIEvents.OnCoinChanged` khi coin thay đổi

```diff
-public class CoinManager : Singleton<CoinManager>
+public class CoinManager : Persistence<CoinManager>
 {
     public void AddCoin(float amount) {
         totalCoins += amount;
+        UIEvents.OnCoinChanged?.Invoke(totalCoins);
     }
     public void RemoveCoin(float amount) {
         totalCoins -= amount;
+        UIEvents.OnCoinChanged?.Invoke(totalCoins);
     }
 }
```

